description: [``botocore``] Support for generating code that is compatible with future versions of amplify project dependencies.
[``botocore``] Adds support for sending WebRTC audio to Amazon Kineses Video Streams.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for application-wide default job configurations.
[``botocore``] Adding sensitive trait to attributes. Change max SessionDuration from 720 to 60. Correct "ApiAccess" attribute to "apiAccess" to maintain consistency between APIs.
[``botocore``] Added ability to tag users upon creation.
[``botocore``] This release updates the enum values for ResourceType in SSM DescribeInstanceInformation input and ConnectionStatus in GetConnectionStatus output.
[``botocore``] You can now perform an exact match against the web request's JA3 fingerprint.
